{"title":"2020-04-02","virtualPath":"/Diary/","html":"<p>桜のシーズン</p>\n<p><a href=\"img/2020/2020-04-02/20200402-174655-P_20200402_174655_vHDR_Auto_HP.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"img/2020/2020-04-02/20200402-174655-P_20200402_174655_vHDR_Auto_HP.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"公園\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"></a></p>\n<p>路駐レイドの聖地、駅西ジムでパトちゃんご立腹。可憐なギャル婦警さんが交通整理してた。制服ぶかぶかだし。</p>\n<p><a href=\"img/2020/2020-04-02/20200402-181812-P_20200402_181812_vHDR_Auto.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"img/2020/2020-04-02/20200402-181812-P_20200402_181812_vHDR_Auto.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"パト\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"></a></p>\n<p>金沢駅前</p>\n<p><a href=\"img/2020/2020-04-02/20200402-200831-P_20200402_200830_vHDR_Auto.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"img/2020/2020-04-02/20200402-200831-P_20200402_200830_vHDR_Auto.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"></a></p>\n<hr>\n<p>初ランドロスは 2/4。今日は歩きながらだったから確率悪い。</p>\n<hr>\n<p>PokemonGo V0.171.2-G release</p>\n","styles":["/css/github-markdown.css","/css/markdown-include.css"],"description":"日記","updated":"2020-04-05T13:41:52","published":"2020-04-05T13:41:52"}